-- New Orleans Saints Coach and General Manager Apologize for Bounty System
-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 2012-03-06T22:26:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-06/new-orleans-saints-coach-and-general-manager-apologize-for-bounty-system.html
New Orleans Saints coach Sean Payton
and General Manager Mickey Loomis apologized today for the
bounty system under which players were paid bonuses to injure
members of opposing teams.  “We acknowledge that the violations disclosed by the NFL
during their investigation of our club happened under our
watch,” Payton and Loomis said in a joint statement released by
the team. “We take full responsibility.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  